<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='360240' id='t-360240'>we got to know Mouaz's story.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='363320' id='t-363320'>He was born in the Syrian capital
of Damascus in 1991.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='367240' id='t-367240'>He was raised in a middle class family,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='369122' id='t-369122'>and his father in the middle there
is a chemical engineer</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='371813' id='t-371813'>who spent 11 years in prison for belonging
