<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='381040' id='t-381040'>They said he was that kind of guy.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='383040' id='t-383040'>Mouaz studied to become
an electrical engineer</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='385840' id='t-385840'>at the University of Damascus.</span>
