<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='652760' id='t-652760'>And to me, and probably a lot of you,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='654560' id='t-654560'>a better life would mean</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='656160' id='t-656160'>being able to do more
