so many resources for this story,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='823800' id='t-823800'>which tells a lot about newspapers
taking the responsibility,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='826682' id='t-826682'>but how did you sell it to your editors?</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:01
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='830360' id='t-830360'>Anders Fjellberg: It wasn't easy at first,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='832400' id='t-832400'>because we weren't able to know
what we actually could figure out.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='836400' id='t-836400'>As soon as it became clear</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='837680' id='t-837680'>that we actually could be able
to identify who the first one was,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='842160' id='t-842160'>we basically got the message
that we could do whatever we wanted,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='845240' id='t-845240'>just travel wherever you need to go,
do whatever you need to do,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='848280' id='t-848280'>just get this done.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:22
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='851720' id='t-851720'>BG: That's an editor
taking responsibility.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='854080' id='t-854080'>The story, by the way,
has been translated and published</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='856724' id='t-856724'>across several European countries,
and certainly will continue to do.</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='860000' id='t-860000'>And we want to read the updates from you.
Thank you Anders. Thank you Tomm.</span>
</span>
</p>
<p class='talk-transcript__para'>
<data class='talk-transcript__para__time'>
14:34
</data>
<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='863560' id='t-863560'>(Applause)</span>
</span>
</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
